entry.title: anyonlabs/Snowflake.jl
entry.summary: Snowflake is an open source Julia-based software library for implementing quantum circuits, and then running them on quantum computers and quantum simulators. The project is sponsored by Anyon Systems, Inc. See https://anyonlabs.github.io/Snowflake.jl/dev for the latest documentation.
